title: AHS Apocalypse Episode 4 Review SPOILERS!!
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This season has been absolutely incredible so far
At this point, they've snatched our whole skulls away tbh.
Queenie and Cordelia honestly made me really sad

As always got those season ties
Murder House: queenie trying to escape hotel just like Violet trying to escape murder house
Asylum: classic case of demonic possession 
Coven: warlocks, seven wonders, Cordelia’s publicity tour, coven theme tune, so many references ❤️
" I always thought the world would end with fire and ice, not witches and warlocks! " - the Great, Myrtle Snow! S8 E4= 10 out of 10
